title: "Website Cloner — Claude AI Skill"
abstract: >
  A Claude AI Skill that clones any website into a pixel-perfect, self-contained
  HTML/CSS/JS file using Claude AI. Supports GSAP animations and Tailwind CSS.
  Built for web developers, designers, and AI enthusiasts who want to recreate
  website layouts without manual coding.
